The paper deals with the problem of collaborative ranking, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep learning models such as RNN, CNN, and Transformers, as well as attention mechanisms, places the paper in the subfields of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
